SimStream Site Components

- Login System
	- Username
	- Password
	- Type (Admin (us), Educator, Student, Other)
	- Profile
	- Contact Information (if Educator OR make it optional)

- Projects
	- Browser Scratch Player
	- Description
	- Author
	- Tag (part of a group OR contextual tag)
	- Comments

- Groups
	- Group Creator/Leader
	- Members of Group
	- Group Page
		- Name of Group (Focus, Title, Context)
		- Feeds (Recent projects, recent discussions)

- Curriculum
	- Focus
	- Learning Objectives
	- Prior Knowledge
	- Scratch Activity

- Discussion (Forums)
	- Educator Forums
	- Other Forums

- Resources
	- Scratch Website
	- Scratch Ed


SimStream is the first "Group" on the site.